schedule.pizza
==============

easiest way to find a time. Designed for agents, built for humans.

API
---

::

    GET  /api/v1/availability?user={username}&code={booking_code}
    POST /api/v1/schedule
    POST /api/v1/recommend
    POST /api/v1/book
    POST /api/v1/book-group
    GET  /api/v1

Development
-----------

::

    pnpm install
    pnpm dev
    pnpm smoke
    SCHEDULE_PIZZA_URL=https://schedule.pizza \
      SCHEDULE_PIZZA_SMOKE_USER={username} \
      SCHEDULE_PIZZA_SMOKE_CODE={booking_code} \
      pnpm smoke-authorized
    SCHEDULE_PIZZA_URL=https://schedule.pizza \
      SCHEDULE_PIZZA_SMOKE_URL={booking_url} \
      pnpm smoke-authorized
    SCHEDULE_PIZZA_URL=https://schedule.pizza \
      SCHEDULE_PIZZA_SMOKE_URL={booking_url} \
      SCHEDULE_PIZZA_SMOKE_SESSION_COOKIE={better_auth_cookie} \
      pnpm smoke-authorized
    SCHEDULE_PIZZA_URL=https://schedule.pizza \
      SCHEDULE_PIZZA_SMOKE_URL={booking_url} \
      SCHEDULE_PIZZA_SMOKE_WRITE=1 \
      SCHEDULE_PIZZA_SMOKE_BOOKER_EMAIL={booker_email} \
      SCHEDULE_PIZZA_SMOKE_SESSION_COOKIE={better_auth_cookie} \
      pnpm smoke-authorized
    SCHEDULE_PIZZA_LIVE_SMOKE=1 \
      SCHEDULE_PIZZA_URL=https://schedule.pizza \
      SCHEDULE_PIZZA_LIVE_SMOKE_USER={username} \
      SCHEDULE_PIZZA_LIVE_SMOKE_BOOKER_EMAIL={booker_email} \
      pnpm smoke-live
    pnpm build
    pnpm deploy

Use a real booking code for authorized smoke checks. Failed code checks are
rate-limited. A session cookie checks signed-in host APIs. Use the full signed
browser cookie, usually `__Secure-better-auth.session_token=...` on production;
the raw `session.token` database value is not a valid cookie. Write smoke
creates one booking and cancels it through the host account session.

Live smoke is an operator check for production. It creates a temporary booking
code in D1, books one individual slot and one group slot through the public API,
deletes the Google Calendar events, marks the rows cancelled, and revokes the
temporary code. It refuses to run unless `SCHEDULE_PIZZA_LIVE_SMOKE=1`.

